title: SPY + RYAN BURCH | CROSSTOWN COLLECTION
description:
Ryan Burch is a rare species—a young pro surfer that not only shapes his own equipment, but questions and pushes design to new, truly unique places. Often seen anywhere from Cardiff to Bali riding anything from homemade 9'6" logs to a 4' block of foam, take in the intricacies surrounding Burch's love of board design and reeling point breaks over a pot of jet black java.

Explore the entire Crosstown Collection here: http://www.spyoptic.com/crosstown
